<html>
<style>
.emailbody {
    font-family: Arial,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,sans-serif; 
    border: 2px solid skyblue;
    padding:10px;
    border-radius:10px;
}
.niceTable tr td { 
    padding:8px 
}
.smallPrint {
    font-size:-2;
}
</style>
<body>
<div class="emailbody">
<!--TEMPLATE NewTopic.htm-->
<p>Workspace: <a href="{$wsURL}">{$wsName|onempty(Unnamed Workspace)|html}</a>
&nbsp; Action Item: <a href="{{actionItemURL}}">{{actionItem.synopsis}}</a></p>
<hr/>
<p>
{% if ($isFinal) %}
Action item has been closed as <b>{$actionItem.state}</b>:
{% elseif ($isFuture) %}
Action item is marked to be done in the future: 
{% elseif ($recipientIsAssignedTask) %}
Action item is assigned to you:
{% else %}
Action item has recently changed state or assignees: 
{% endif %}
</p>

<table class="niceTable">
<tr>
    <td>Synopsis:</td>
    <td><a href="{$actionItemURL}">{$actionItem.synopsis|onempty(No Synopsis)|html}}</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Requested by:</td> 
    <td>{% loop in $actionItem.requesters as user}{$user}{% divider %}, {% endloop %}</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Assigned to:</td>
    <td>{% loop in $actionItem.assignTo as user}{$user.name}{% divider %}, {% endloop %}</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Description:</td>
    <td>{$actionItem.description}</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>State:</td>
    <td>{$stateName}</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Due:</td>
    <td>{$actionItem.duedate|date(yyyy-MM-dd)}</td>
</tr>
</table>

</div>

<div class="smallPrint">
This message was sent to {$optout.emailId|html}.
{% if ($optout.isIndividualRequest) %}
    You have received this message in order to carry out the request that you made.  
{% elseif ($optout.isSuperAdmin) %}
    You have received this message because you are a registered 'super admin' for this server. 
    If you want to avoid getting these messages in the future please work with the server 
    administrator to change that.
{% elseif ($optout.isDirectAddress) %}    
    You have received this message because the sender entered your email address 
    directly into the address prompt and not due to any automated email mechanism. 
{% elseif ($optout.roleName) %}
    You have received this message because you are a player of the 
    <b>{$optout.roleName|html}</b> role in the 
    <a href="{$optout.wsURL}">{$optout.wsName|onempty(Unnamed)|html}</a> workspace.
{% endif %}
{% if ($optout.leaveRole) %}
You can <a href="{$optout.leaveRole}">withdraw from that role</a> if you no 
longer want to be involved and receive email for the role. 
{% endif %}
{% if ($optout.unsubscribe) %}
To change the types of e-mail communication you receive in future, you can 
<a href="{$optout.unsubscribe}">alter your subscriptions</a>. 
{% else %}
You have not created a profile or have not associated 
<a href="{$baseURL}/v/FindPerson.htm?uid={$optout.emailId|url}">{$optout.emailId|html}</a> 
with any existing profile.
{% endif %}
</div>


</body></html>
